# Production build-time configuration for the SPA (Cloudflare Pages).
#
# VITE_API_URL is the origin of the deployed FastAPI backend. It is baked into
# the bundle at `pnpm build` (Vite inlines VITE_* vars), so the static SPA on
# Pages calls the cross-origin API at ${VITE_API_URL}/api/v1/... instead of the
# dev-only Vite proxy. Leave it UNSET in dev — the empty base keeps requests
# same-origin so the proxy in vite.config.ts forwards /api to localhost:8400.
#
# No trailing slash (the client strips it anyway). Set the real value in the
# Cloudflare Pages project's build environment variables, not in a committed file.
VITE_API_URL=https://cloudy-api.fly.dev
